# QuizzyBackEnd

This is the backend for Quizzy an api for making and taking quizzes. 

## User Collection [/user]

### Create User [Post]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Body 
    {
        "username" : "me",
        "password": "me"
    }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
    {
        "id": 1
    }


## Questions Collection [/questions]

